casebody.data:
CHRISTINE FALLS OF NEW YORK, INC., et al., petitioners
v.
ALGONQUIN POWER INCOME FUND, et al. No. 13-349. Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 2, 2013. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied. Justice SOTOMAYOR took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
